{"tid":2444048,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聶德權：對公務員可否持有外國護照及BNO 黨中央暫未有批示","createTime":"2021-03-12T12:23:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T14:25:16.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"00e16ed5997a0e4e47c585da5207e280400db81e","tid":2444048,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T12:23:08.000Z","msg":"聶德權：人大的決定將香港選舉制度重新放入正確軌道<br />\n<br />\n工聯會在土瓜灣設簽名街站，呼籲市民支持全國人大的決定，完善選舉制度。<br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局局長聶德權到場支持，表示人大的決定確保進入政治體制的人符合愛國者要求，並了解香港是國家不可分割的一部分，尊重和接受國家的根本制度為社會主義制度，維護憲法和基本法下的憲制秩序。<br />\n<br />\n聶德權認為，一國是兩制的前提和基礎，能維護國家安全、主權以及發展利益。完善選舉制度的決定是將選舉制度重新放入正確軌道，行政長官以及立法會的選舉辦法按實際情況和循序漸進的原則而規定，因此選舉制度並沒有倒退，反而能讓更多有能力之士，願意加入政治體制。<br />\n<br />\n至於愛國者治港的標準，會否要求公務員不得持有外國護照及BNO等，聶德權表示，對於各種完善制度的建議，會在有共識下進行討論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580304-20210312.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580304-20210312.htm&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXI2%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=d6f097a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580304-20210312.htm&h=ccadeaf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580304-20210312.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1f79ac646b7ca09a603c26fcc9c2142534a07030","tid":2444048,"uid":2054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T12:26:38.000Z","msg":"做公墓員效忠英女王<br />\n食兩家茶禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FXN4SNMKOYKWPQ3ZN7BVPBQM4U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFXN4SNMKOYKWPQ3ZN7BVPBQM4U.jpg&h=a68a3599&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c33c83be7088ca2578c4b2751bb09a0900145d0a","tid":2444048,"uid":279938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T12:28:46.000Z","msg":"「批」佢老母「示」，叫共匪收埋佢份人工啦"},{"pid":"94b291c80fc439c37d6bf0634d24b2383b91b9ff","tid":2444048,"uid":308440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T12:34:57.000Z","msg":"唔駛急都未用完你班tempo, 用完就輪到你地啦"},{"pid":"f94e3bce44d2cf15c7ec91cbedbad674922ae577","tid":2444048,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T13:21:31.000Z","msg":"未用完梗係唔討論<br />\n你唔係以為共產黨真係會放過你呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c837938f043dfedf7cbb3d7088b38aa10ca116a7","tid":2444048,"uid":71511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T14:25:16.000Z","msg":"唔使討論，全港市民嘅聲音就係全體公務員要愛國辭黨，放棄bno 同外國護照係理所當然嘅事，要效忠就必須心中只有黨"}]}